               <pb facs="OGA_Gams_Nr_191b_1"/>
               <div>
                  <seg><add place="left margin">Copia</add></seg>
                  <p><lb/>Wir, landtamman und rath beyder hoch<lb break="no"/>loblichen ohrten <orgName
                     ref="org003265">Schweitz</orgName> und <orgName ref="org003239">Glaruß</orgName>, thun
                     <lb/>kundt und zu wissen mäniglichen, daß in <lb/>der herrschafft <placeName
                        ref="loc006040.09">Hochen Sachsen und Gambs</placeName> macht <lb/>und gewalt erlangt
                     haben, von allem dem <lb/>jenigen, was in dero land- und herrschafft <lb/><term
                        ref="lem001145">steeg und weeg</term> gebrauchen, den <term ref="lem000349">zoll</term>
                     einzu<lb break="no"/>ziechen, gleichförmig wie an anderen <lb/>ohrten auch geschichet,
                     alles fleissig bey hocher <lb/>straff und ungnad bezahlen und erlegen <lb/>solle, wie
                     hernach folget:</p>
                  <p>
                     <table>
                        <row>
                           <cell/>
                           <cell role="label">kreützer</cell>
                           <cell role="label">pfenig</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <cell><lb/>Erstlich von <measure type="volume" quantity="1" unit="Sack"
                              commodity="grain">einem sakh korn</measure>
                              <lb/>gibt mann <term ref="lem000349">zoll</term>
                           </cell>
                           <cell>1</cell>
                           <cell>–</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <cell><lb/>ein <term ref="lem000579">pferdt</term>, so theür es verkaufft
                              wird, <lb/>von jedem gulden</cell>
                           <cell>1</cell>
                           <cell>–</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <cell><lb/>ein stuckh <term ref="lem002693">rindvich</term></cell>
                           <cell>1</cell>
                           <cell>–</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <cell><lb/>von einem <term ref="lem000055">schaff</term>, <term
                              ref="lem001394">geiß</term>, <term ref="lem003274.04">bokh</term> oder <term
                                 ref="lem000057">schwein</term></cell>
                           <cell>2</cell>
                           <cell>–</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <cell><lb/><measure commodity="salt" quantity="1" unit="Saum" type="volume"
                              >ein saum saltz</measure></cell>
                           <cell role="data">1</cell>
                           <cell role="data">–</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <cell><lb/><measure quantity="1" commodity="wine" unit="Fuder"
                              type="undefined">ein fueder wein</measure></cell>
                           <cell role="data">4</cell>
                           <cell role="data">2</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <cell>
                              <lb/><measure quantity="1" commodity="wine" unit="Saum" type="volume">ein saum
                                 wein</measure> zu <term ref="lem001069">roß</term></cell>
                           <cell role="data">–</cell>
                           <cell role="data">2</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <cell><lb/>ein <sic>einige</sic>
                              <term ref="lem000071">lagel</term></cell>
                           <cell role="data">–</cell>
                           <cell role="data">1</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <cell><lb/>ein saum <term ref="lem001748">eisen</term> oder <measure
                              quantity="1" unit="Saum" commodity="steel" type="volume">stachel</measure></cell>
                           <cell role="data">2</cell>
                           <cell role="data">–</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <cell><lb/>ein <term ref="lem012799.02">boschen</term>
                              <term ref="lem001748">eisen</term> oder <term ref="lem002956">stachel</term></cell>
                           <cell role="data">1</cell>
                           <cell role="data">–</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <cell><lb/>ein zentner <term ref="lem002304.05">unschlig</term> oder <measure
                              quantity="1" commodity="cheese" unit="Zentner" type="weight">käß</measure></cell>
                           <cell role="data">1</cell>
                           <cell role="data">2</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <cell><lb/><measure quantity="1" commodity="hemp" unit="Zentner"
                              type="weight">ein zentner hampff</measure></cell>
                           <cell role="data">1</cell>
                           <cell role="data">–</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <cell><lb/><measure commodity="hemp" type="volume" unit="Saum" quantity="1"
                              >ein saum hampff</measure></cell>
                           <cell role="data">2</cell>
                           <cell role="data">–</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <cell><lb/>in <term ref="lem003258">zentner</term>
                              <term ref="lem002306">leim</term></cell>
                           <cell role="data">1</cell>
                           <cell role="data">2</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <cell><lb/>ein zentner <term ref="lem016821.01">weinstein</term></cell>
                           <cell role="data">–</cell>
                           <cell role="data">3</cell>
                        </row>
                     </table></p>
                  <p>
                     <lb/>Von dem originale abgezogen, den <origDate when="1775-06-20">20.<hi rend="sup">ten</hi>
                        juny 1775</origDate>, <lb/>von mir, <persName ref="per004894a">Johann Rudolff
                           Stähelin</persName>, landtvogt <lb/>im <placeName ref="loc000842">Gaster</placeName> und
                     <placeName ref="loc006040">Gambs</placeName>.
                  </p>
               </div>
               <div>
                  <ab type="dorsal" place="verso" hand="hand18c"><lb/>Copia <lb/>der alten getruckten
                     <lb/><term ref="lem001333">zoll tarriffen</term> zu <lb/><placeName ref="loc006040">Gambs</placeName></ab>
               </div>
               <pb facs="OGA_Gams_Nr._191bv"/>
               <div>
                  <ab type="archiving reference" place="verso"><lb/>Nro 191 B, N<hi rend="sup">o</hi> 14, 35,
                     ano 1775</ab>
